---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Fundraising & Financial Strategy | GoldWhite Consulting"
  description="Institutional-grade fundraising support for STEM startups. Financial modelling, pitch materials, investor targeting, and round management. £12M+ raised for clients."
>

  <!-- ═══ HERO ═══ -->
  <section style="min-height:70vh;padding:160px 60px 100px;background:#0F1A2E;position:relative;overflow:hidden;display:flex;align-items:center;">
    <div style="position:absolute;top:-40%;right:-15%;width:800px;height:800px;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(201,168,76,.07) 0%,transparent 70%);border-radius:50%;pointer-events:none;"></div>
    <div style="position:relative;z-index:2;max-width:780px;">
      <div class="anim-1" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C9A84C;margin-bottom:32px;">
        <span style="width:40px;height:1.5px;background:#C9A84C;display:inline-block;"></span>
        01 — Fundraising &amp; Financial Strategy
      </div>
      <h1 class="anim-2" style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:clamp(36px,4.5vw,58px);font-weight:600;line-height:1.12;color:#fff;margin-bottom:28px;">
        Raising capital is one of the highest-stakes activities your startup will undertake.
      </h1>
      <p class="anim-3" style="font-size:18px;line-height:1.75;color:rgba(255,255,255,.6);max-width:640px;">
        We bring institutional-grade financial expertise to the startup world: from pitch materials and financial modelling to investor targeting and round management.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ THE CHALLENGE ═══ -->
  <section style="padding:120px 60px;background:#F8F6F1;">
    <div style="max-width:800px;margin:0 auto;">
      <div class="reveal" style="font-size:12px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:2.5px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C9A84C;margin-bottom:20px;">The Challenge</div>
      <h2 class="reveal" style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:clamp(28px,3vw,40px);font-weight:600;line-height:1.2;color:#0F1A2E;margin-bottom:40px;">When scientific credibility isn't enough to close a round</h2>
      <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:24px;">
        <p class="reveal" style="font-size:17px;line-height:1.8;color:#4A5568;">Most STEM founders are world-class scientists or engineers. Fundraising is a different skill. The gap between having a strong technical proposition and presenting a compelling investment case is where many strong companies lose months and momentum.</p>
        <p class="reveal reveal-delay-1" style="font-size:17px;line-height:1.8;color:#4A5568;">Investors are pattern-matching at speed. Your pitch deck, your financial model, your narrative structure, and your ability to handle diligence questions all have to be investor-grade before you go to market. Getting it wrong costs you dilution, credibility, and time you don't have.</p>
        <p class="reveal reveal-delay-2" style="font-size:17px;line-height:1.8;color:#4A5568;">We have raised over £12M for clients across pre-seed to Series B, and we have sat on both sides of the table. We know what investors need to see. We help you get there before you start the process, not during it.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ WHAT WE DELIVER ═══ -->
  <section style="padding:120px 60px;background:#fff;">
    <div style="max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;">
      <div class="reveal" style="font-size:12px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:2.5px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C9A84C;margin-bottom:20px;">What We Deliver</div>
      <h2 class="reveal" style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:clamp(28px,3vw,40px);font-weight:600;line-height:1.2;color:#0F1A2E;margin-bottom:56px;">The full fundraising stack, from narrative to close.</h2>
      <div style="border-left:3px solid #C9A84C;padding-left:40px;">
        {[
          { label: 'Financial modelling and valuation', desc: 'Building robust, investor-ready financial models that tell your growth story with clarity and credibility.' },
          { label: 'Pitch materials', desc: 'Creating compelling pitch decks, one-pagers, and data rooms that stand out in a crowded market.' },
          { label: 'Investor targeting and introductions', desc: 'Identifying the right investors for your stage, sector, and geography, and facilitating warm introductions through our network.' },
          { label: 'Round management', desc: 'Running structured fundraising processes, managing investor communications, and advising on term sheet negotiations.' },
          { label: 'Grant applications', desc: 'Preparing and submitting applications to Innovate UK, UKRI, Horizon Europe, and other grant bodies.' },
          { label: 'Cash-flow management', desc: 'Designing financial controls and forecasting systems to extend your runway and reduce burn rate.' },
        ].map(({ label, desc }, i, arr) => (
          <div class="reveal" style={`padding:24px 0;${i < arr.length - 1 ? 'border-bottom:1px solid #E2E0DB;' : ''}`}>
            <div style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:17px;font-weight:600;color:#0F1A2E;margin-bottom:8px;">{label}</div>
            <p style="font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;color:#4A5568;">{desc}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ WHO THIS IS FOR ═══ -->
  <section style="padding:120px 60px;background:#F8F6F1;">
    <div style="max-width:800px;margin:0 auto;">
      <div class="reveal" style="font-size:12px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:2.5px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C9A84C;margin-bottom:20px;">Who This Is For</div>
      <h2 class="reveal" style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:clamp(28px,3vw,40px);font-weight:600;line-height:1.2;color:#0F1A2E;margin-bottom:40px;">Right for you if…</h2>
      <div class="reveal" style="background:rgba(201,168,76,0.07);border:1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.22);border-left:3px solid #C9A84C;border-radius:6px;padding:32px 36px;">
        <ul style="list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:16px;">
          {[
            'Healthtech, medtech, and diagnostics companies preparing to raise',
            'Pre-seed to Series B startups preparing to raise capital',
            'Companies that need to restructure their financial story',
            'Teams without a CFO or with limited fundraising experience',
          ].map(item => (
            <li style="font-size:16px;color:#4A5568;display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:12px;line-height:1.6;">
              <span style="width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:#C9A84C;margin-top:7px;flex-shrink:0;display:inline-block;"></span>
              {item}
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ HOW WE WORK ═══ -->
  <section style="padding:120px 60px;background:#fff;">
    <div style="max-width:800px;margin:0 auto;">
      <div class="reveal" style="font-size:12px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:2.5px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C9A84C;margin-bottom:20px;">How We Work</div>
      <h2 class="reveal" style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:clamp(28px,3vw,40px);font-weight:600;line-height:1.2;color:#0F1A2E;margin-bottom:28px;">Structured for the way fundraising actually works.</h2>
      <p class="reveal" style="font-size:17px;line-height:1.8;color:#4A5568;max-width:680px;">We typically work on fundraising engagements as defined projects with a clear scope and timeline: from initial narrative development through to investor process management. For companies earlier in the journey, we also offer retained advisory to build fundraising readiness over time.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ CTA ═══ -->
  <section style="padding:120px 60px;background:#0F1A2E;text-align:center;position:relative;overflow:hidden;">
    <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background:radial-gradient(ellipse at center,rgba(201,168,76,.08) 0%,transparent 70%);pointer-events:none;"></div>
    <div class="reveal" style="position:relative;z-index:2;max-width:600px;margin:0 auto;">
      <h2 style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:clamp(34px,4vw,48px);font-weight:600;color:#fff;margin-bottom:20px;">Ready to start your raise?</h2>
      <p style="font-size:17px;line-height:1.7;color:rgba(255,255,255,.5);margin-bottom:40px;">Every engagement starts with a conversation. Book a 30-minute strategy call with one of our directors. No pitch, no obligation.</p>
      <a
        href="/contact"
        style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;background:#C9A84C;color:#0F1A2E;padding:18px 40px;border-radius:8px;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;font-size:16px;letter-spacing:.3px;transition:all .3s;"
        onmouseover="this.style.background='#E0C777';this.style.transform='translateY(-2px)';this.style.boxShadow='0 8px 30px rgba(201,168,76,.3)'"
        onmouseout="this.style.background='#C9A84C';this.style.transform='none';this.style.boxShadow='none'"
      >Book a Strategy Call →</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
